node.text:
On that demon time, she might start a OF 👀 @realllyjen 

Fun fact lol, I was 19 here 🥵 I took this pic a month before my 20th Birthday and days after that, I booked a One-Way flight to Colombia! **STORYTIME COMING SOON** 

It’s one of my fav pictures cause this was literally where my journey to self love began for me 🤍 I think it’s time for another photoshoot tho and of course another crazy ass adventure lol, where should I go? 🌎
